      "title": "Today's power cut timetable",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Public Utilities Commission has announced that the three-hour power cut will take effect today (28).",
        "For ABCD, EFGH, IJKL, PQRS, TUVW, the power outage will be 1 hour 40 minutes during the day and 1 hour 20 minutes at night.",
        "It has been announced that a 2 hour power cut will be implemented in CC zones from 6 am to 8 pm and a 3 hour power cut will be implemented in MNOXYZ zones from 5 am to 8 am."
      ],
